************position**********
- position: mac dinh la static
- Khi su dung cac position khac static co the ap dung voi cac thuoc tinh dieu huong
- position: absolute an theo vi tri cua cha khi va chi khi cha co position : relative
- position: fixed => can theo khung trinh duyet VD: co dinh menu, banner quang cao
- position: stiky => can theo the cha
- Khi su dung relative : no roi vi tri nhung van de lai khoang trong

******************
header, div: group selector
- boxsizing: border-box: ngan chan viec anh huong cua cac yeu to khac



*******Grid******
grid-template-rows: x x: quy dinh so hang
grid-template-columns: y y y

grid-row-start:chon diem bat dau cua o
grid-row-end: chon diem ket thuc cua o

row-gap: khoang cach giua cac o


********flex*****
flex-shrink: 0 tu dong thay doi khi giam
flex-grow: 0 tu dong thay doi khi tang
flex-basis: 100px: co dinh kich thuoc
flex-direction: đảo phần tử theo trục main-axis: row, row-reverse
align-self: đảo phần tử theo trục cross-axis

- de su dung algin-content phai su dụng flex-wrap